  "prompt": "Why do I care so much about everything?",
  "response": "There could be several reasons why you feel deeply about many things:\n\n1. Emotional sensitivity\n- You may have a naturally empathetic personality\n- High emotional intelligence\n- Heightened awareness of surroundings and people's feelings\n\n2. Psychological factors\n- Past experiences that have made you more sensitive\n- Anxiety or fear of potential negative outcomes\n- Desire for control or perfectionism\n- Low self-esteem leading to overthinking\n\n3. Personal traits\n- Highly compassionate nature\n- Strong sense of responsibility\n- Tendency to be introspective\n- Desire to make a positive impact\n\n4. Potential mental health considerations\n- Generalized anxiety disorder\n- Highly sensitive person (HSP) trait\n- Empathic personality type\n\nSome potential coping strategies:\n- Practice mindfulness\n- Set healthy emotional boundaries\n- Learn stress management techniques\n- Develop self-care routines\n- Consider therapy to explore underlying reasons\n\nWould you like to discuss which of these might resonate with your specific experience?",
